got? Why, it’s the perfect recipe for a delicious beef and couscous tagine!

*Keep an eye out...
Due to recent sourcing
challenges, we’ve replaced
leek with courgette, which
may be a little different to
what’s pictured. Don’t worry,
your recipe will be just
as delicious!*
